Reproducing figure 4 panel c

Load the metadata of each interaction and plot spatial heatmaps.

library(ggplot2)

meta.dir = "your_data_path"
meta.list = list.files(meta.dir, pattern = "MetaData", full.names = T)

intr.change = c("Dll1-Notch1", "Fgf8-Fgfr1", "Spp1-Cd44", "Efna3-Epha5", "Igf2-Igf2r")
names(intr.change) = c("DLL1-NOTC1", "FGF8-FGFR1", "OSTP-CD44", "EFNA3-EPHA5", "IGF2-MPRI")

for (i in meta.list){
  i.str = stringr::str_split(i, "_")[[1]]
  INTR = i.str[[length(i.str)]]
  INTR = gsub(".rds", "", INTR)

  meta = readRDS(i)
  # min-max scaling
  meta$CytoSignal = (meta$CytoSignal - min(meta$CytoSignal)) / (max(meta$CytoSignal) - min(meta$CytoSignal))
  meta$LIANA = (meta$LIANA - min(meta$LIANA)) / (max(meta$LIANA) - min(meta$LIANA))
  meta$SpatialDM = (meta$SpatialDM - min(meta$SpatialDM)) / (max(meta$SpatialDM) - min(meta$SpatialDM))
  meta$NICHES = (meta$NICHES - min(meta$NICHES)) / (max(meta$NICHES) - min(meta$NICHES))
  meta$stLearn = (meta$stLearn - min(meta$stLearn)) / (max(meta$stLearn) - min(meta$stLearn))
  meta = meta[meta$region == "roi", ]
  
  # mutate to add type
  plot.df <- tidyr::pivot_longer(meta, cols = c("CytoSignal", "LIANA", "SpatialDM", "NICHES", "stLearn"), 
                names_to = "type", values_to = "value")

  p1 = ggplot(plot.df, aes(x = x, y = y, color = value)) +
    geom_point(size = 0.8, stroke = 0.2) +
    facet_wrap(~type, nrow = 2, ncol = 3) +
    scale_color_viridis_c(option = "C", direction = -1, ) +
    cowplot::theme_cowplot(12) +
    theme(axis.title = element_blank(),
      axis.text = element_blank(),
      axis.ticks = element_blank(),
      legend.position = "none") +
    coord_fixed() +
    ggtitle(paste0("Interaction: ", intr.change[INTR]))

  print(p1)

}
